{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Egypt many years ago, Saint Anthony the Monk is visited by an Angel and told to go into the wilderness to find the Righteous Hermit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player attacks using his staff with limited stamina, so time your attacks wisely.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player has the ability to climb platforms that are too high to jump on.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Avoid the traps &amp; any demonic surprise attacks at every corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ravens will randomly drop bread from the sky to increase your health.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete the level before time runs out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn about the backstory of the Monk as you complete levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(This is Alpha 1, certain features will change in the future)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739054536","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435440/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739054536","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435440/4aca3f222589605cbacfcef6063dd96813c68ae8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739054536","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435440/4aca3f222589605cbacfcef6063dd96813c68ae8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739054536","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Egypt many years ago, Saint Anthony the Monk is visited by an Angel and told to go into the wilde